MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Disguise_a_scheme_in_shadows_cast
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 127
  mythName: Disguise a scheme in shadows cast
  omens:
  - '1. The Thorn Seer roams the Realm,

    proclaiming an invasion of great scuttling

    monsters
    is coming soon.'
  - '2. A messenger declares that the Thorn Seer

    has reclaimed a lost fortress
    (in the Myth

    Hex), creating an impenetrable sanctuary

    for when the
    invasion comes.'
  - '3. Three claw swarm cutters peer from their

    tunnels, scouts for the invasion.
    If seen

    they scutter back underground.'
  - '4. A smith and her three young apprentices

    are looking for a new home.
    They left the

    Fortress, as the Thorn Seer wanted the

    impossible from
    them, demanding whole

    walls of iron be built.'
  - '5. The voice of the Thorn Seer is heard

    across the land. The invasion is
    here,

    numberless hordes of the claw swarm

    attacking the Fortress. They
    will not

    actually breach the Fortress, as they are

    creations of the
    Thorn Seer.'
  - '6. The invasion defeated, the Thorn Seer

    demands to be made ruler of the
    Realm,

    the Fortress as his Seat of Power.'
  verse: 'Omens

    1. The Thorn Seer roams the Realm,

    proclaiming an invasion
    of great scuttling

    monsters is coming soon.

    2. A messenger declares
    that the Thorn Seer

    has reclaimed a lost fortress (in the Myth

    Hex),
    creating an impenetrable sanctuary

    for when the invasion comes.

    3.
    Three claw swarm cutters peer from their

    tunnels, scouts for the invasion.
    If seen

    they scutter back underground.

    4. A smith and her three young
    apprentices

    are looking for a new home. They left the

    Fortress, as
    the Thorn Seer wanted the

    impossible from them, demanding whole

    walls
    of iron be built.

    5. The voice of the Thorn Seer is heard

    across the
    land. The invasion is here,

    numberless hordes of the claw swarm

    attacking
    the Fortress. They will not

    actually breach the Fortress, as they are

    creations
    of the Thorn Seer.

    6. The invasion defeated, the Thorn Seer

    demands
    to be made ruler of the Realm,

    the Fortress as his Seat of Power.

    Cast

    The
    Thorn Seer

    VIG 9, CLA 16, SPI 14, 3 GD

    A2 (thorny body, helm)

    Spined
    mace (d8 hefty), dagger (d6)

    Sees pain in the past and the future.

    Claw
    Swarm Cutter

    VIG 9, CLA 9, SPI 3, 3 GD

    A1 (green carapace)

    Claws
    (2d6), acid spit (d8)

    Cunning instinct (see below).

    Claw Swarm Hulk

    VIG
    15, CLA 5, SPI 5, 6 GD

    A2 (red carapace)

    Great claws (2d8), blunt instinct

    A
    cage in stone, all thorned and vast'
  castEntries:
  - name: The Thorn Seer
    statBlock: 'VIG 9, CLA 16, SPI 14, 3 GD

      A2 (thorny body, helm)'
    notes: 'Spined mace (d8 hefty), dagger (d6)

      Sees pain in the past and
      the future.'
  - name: Claw Swarm Cutter
    statBlock: 'VIG 9, CLA 9, SPI 3, 3 GD

      A1 (green carapace)'
    notes: 'Claws (2d6), acid spit (d8)

      Cunning instinct (see below).'
  - name: Claw Swarm Hulk
    statBlock: 'VIG 15, CLA 5, SPI 5, 6 GD

      A2 (red carapace)'
    notes: 'Great claws (2d8), blunt instinct

      A cage in stone, all thorned
      and vast

      Disguise a scheme in shadows cast

      CUNNING INSTINCTS

      Action
      Objective

      1 Burrow Regroup later

      2 Scatter Surprise the enemy

      3
      Camouflage Target a single enemy

      4 Sprout wings Confuse the enemy

      5
      Spawn more Set up an advantage

      6 Spit acid Exploit a weak spot

      Fortress

      Dwelling:
      Exile pottery ~ Sanctum: Timeless cavern ~ Monument: Lyre tree

      Hazard:
      Numb ache on the air ~ Curse: The Silence ~ Ruin: Scoured trail

      Th'
  flavorTable:
    title: CUNNING INSTINCTS
    rows:
    - 1 Burrow Regroup later
    - 2 Scatter Surprise the enemy
    - 3 Camouflage Target a single enemy
    - 4 Sprout wings Confuse the enemy
    - 5 Spawn more Set up an advantage
    - '6 Spit acid Exploit a weak spot

      Fortress'
  dwelling: Exile pottery
  sanctum: Timeless cavern
  monument: Lyre tree
  hazard: Numb ache on the air
  curse: The Silence
  ruin: Scoured trail
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
